long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides miscellaneous views for GitLab time tracking data
This item adds a button to GitLab "issues" page, which allows the user to generate and download time logs data reports. Pressing the button opens the form which allows to select specific GitLab user, project and time range, which will be set for the report. 
If users want to get GitLab issues time logging reports for analytics and other purposes in convenient xlsx format without putting additional efforts in gathering data using different GitLab interfaces they should use this item.
